    "title": "Lead Instructional Designer at IIM Ahmedabad",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at IIM Ahmedabad. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Instructional Designer to strengthen our Varanasi-based team.\n\nAbout IIM Ahmedabad:\nIIM Ahmedabad is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Develop and deliver engaging lesson plans for students\n• Create curriculum-aligned learning materials and assessments\n• Conduct doubt-clearing sessions and remedial classes for weak students\n• Contribute to school newsletter, blogs, and other publications\n• Support students with special educational needs\n• Utilize technology and digital tools to enhance learning outcomes\n• Participate in teacher training and professional development programs\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Pedagogy\n• Proficiency in Lesson Planning\n• Proficiency in Communication Skills\n• Proficiency in Data Analysis\n• Proficiency in Mentoring\n• Proficiency in E-learning\n• Proficiency in Curriculum Development\n• Proficiency in Classroom Management\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Varanasi, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with IIM Ahmedabad!",
